{"tid":1347790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔理有意定無意，啲黑再咁拖長搞落去，義士21號做嘅野就功虧一簣","createTime":"2019-07-22T06:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:08:32.000Z","uid":53349,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b83775c5c813508bd56379b1de5d8bdd6366d80","tid":1347790,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:46:43.000Z","msg":"咁我哋依家應該做既係邊樣？<br />\n<br />\n1. 利用呢段時間整合文宣資料，等黑嗰面完哂先一野谷返21號啲料出黎<br />\n<br />\n2. 日日都推21號嘅料出黎<br />\n<br />\n邊個方法影響力大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"8872e2d4e3f03c2a11279248f35766d45dff5e1a","tid":1347790,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:48:18.000Z","msg":"白衫尋晚一堆等你起底"},{"pid":"8baf1a42b7e0eaad0c1ece86aa1d811c2b684d97","tid":1347790,"uid":53349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:51:57.000Z","msg":"更正，我自己都亂左，我想整合既料係中上環區既料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑嗰邊都唔洗麻煩我哋搞，新聞大把有得講"},{"pid":"1a6c3f5248bd30fd17bed4e22317a329df167194","tid":1347790,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:52:56.000Z","msg":"最緊要將黑社會問題歸根返去黑警同政府就得"},{"pid":"032268827b6a29fe3e5fcc1c17c28a8162f6cb8b","tid":1347790,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a6c3f5248bd30fd17bed4e22317a329df167194","tid":1347790,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:52:56.000Z","msg":"最緊要將黑社會問題歸根返去黑警同政府就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"統一返口徑"},{"pid":"6f987f3fb4177813d04e868f8e9a17abcefbbeaf","tid":1347790,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:54:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d193d9326e1c9f3a289e2cdce2bfa3bc55e5bdd","tid":1347790,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:54:51.000Z","msg":"警黑合作，呢個政權已經顛到放任黑社會周街打人，而警察竟然完全無動於衷，想喺社會上散佈白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n如果大家真係想反抗，要聰明啲，要智勇雙全，我知道香港好多人都係和理非，既然硬碰硬比較難做到，咁破壞香港經濟亦未嘗唔係一個好方法，破壞經濟對一個政權嚟講亦係一個毀滅性打擊，大家之前講嘅<span style=\"color: gold;\">提擠中資銀行、罷工罷市等等不合作運動</span>，其實目的都係破壞經濟<br />\n<br />\n中共作為一個極權，好多錢都會放咗喺維穏費度，既然佢都係用啲錢去對付返人民，我地亦冇必要幫佢維持經濟發展<br />\n<br />\n至於日後如果再有遊行，所有活動應該集中返喺港島，至少都要喺返各區嘅市中心，將矛頭指向政府就可以，話佢地警黑合作（要加上國際文宣），而唔係指向黑幫，有兩大原因：<br />\n<br />\n1.）會演變成群眾鬥群眾嘅局面（中共老伎倆），政府有大好良機可以化身做裁判角色，以平亂之名行維穩之實，將示威者一網打盡，運動隨之瓦解<br />\n<br />\n2.）我上面都講過，黑幫殺人係唔眨眼，落手好狠話殺就殺，而且佢地斬死人付出嘅成本好低，大家唔值得為此而博命，如果係警察無故殺人，同黑幫無故殺人，係兩種完全唔同嘅概念，前者係六四2.0，後者只係一單謀殺案，對政權嘅影響係天差地別"},{"pid":"3bd2cd06d82ed8395d474ea387bfe49cea6c0fd1","tid":1347790,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:29:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48f290dec37cc0005953b6c934f4206d3073d3fe","tid":1347790,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:21:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b7c9586b3358a0a7b140dc5f74c11cdafcabb15","tid":1347790,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb259582e19289491765021d747134b827abe868","tid":1347790,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87OcaGA.jpg&h=5d1b1e66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a12bc5626a05fec18811a6846120141974568d8","tid":1347790,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:05:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"242e7ad88b2f2d8b3185dfcf3b0c0a4aa76f47d9","tid":1347790,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:08:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}